summary: The document appears to be a listing for a vintage Telefunken Hi Fi System from the 1950s, detailing its condition and dimensions. It specifies that the item is available for local pickup in Northern New Jersey and includes a price.
keyFacts: The Telefunken Hi Fi System is from the 1950s and is in excellent condition.
The system has 8 inches of gold trim missing on the upper left side.
The speakers work and the sound quality is described as exceptional.
The dimensions of the system are 48 inches wide, 15.5 inches deep, and 33 inches high.
The item is priced at $1000 and must be picked up, as it will not be shipped.
